### start the application
> sbt run -jvm-debug 9999

### install IntelliJ plugin for scala

### open project in IntelliJ as a BST project

### Menu bar -> Run tab -> edit configuration -> add(+) remote -> set port to 9999 and task name = "play-debug"

### Set break point in where you want to take a look

### Menu bar -> Run tab -> hit "play-debug"

### open browser visiting localhost:9000
